                <expan><abbr>Invic</abbr><ex>to</ex></expan> Deo <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acrum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>pro <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>alute</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sep</abbr><ex>timii</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Valerius et Va<lb break="no" n="4"/>lerianus <expan><abbr>temp</abbr><ex>lum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>vetust</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>conl</abbr><ex>apsum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>inp</abbr><ex>endio</ex></expan> suo <expan><abbr>rest</abbr><ex>ituerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Spuren von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Zahlreiche Ligaturen, auch aus drei Buchstaben. (B): CIMRM: Z. 1: d(eo); Z. 2: Se(ptimi).</p>
